<p>This is a joint BUILDS - PHOTON project. BUILDS is working on a small scale model for PHOTON to take and work with BU to have a large scale model installed in a building on campus (SCI?).</p>

<h3 id="joining">Joining</h3>

<p>If you want to join this project, email John-Nicholas Furst</p>

<h3 id="background-research">Background Research</h3>

<p>Build an Accurate Foucault Pendulum: [<a href="http://www.science-project.com/_members/science-projects/1964/02/1964-02-fs.html">1</a>]</p>

<h3 id="result">Result</h3>

<p>After a consultation with PHOTON BUILDS engineers discussed with PHOTON that they would need approval from structural engineers, BU Facilties, and Boston Building Modifications Board.</p>
